-- BWT Sees Record 2012 Sales and Says First-Quarter Net Jumped
-- B y   J o n a t h a n   T i r o n e
-- 2012-05-11T06:06:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-11/bwt-sees-record-2012-sales-and-says-first-quarter-net-jumped.html
BWT AG (BWT) , the Austrian maker of water
purification technologies, said first-quarter net income rose a
fifth to 4.3 million euros on higher sales.  Full-year revenue “should exceed 500 million euros for the
first time,” BWT said today in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jonathan Tirone at 
 jtirone@bloomberg.net  